title: Suzie (2009) Micheline Lanctot Pascale Bussieres
description:
Imdb id: tt1425249 This is a movie, I have to label it TV because of TPB's filesize rules.

More Micheline Lanctot, this one is a melodrama about a woman trying to care for an autistic boy, the kind who goes into violent screaming fits. Everyone is damaged here; it's insightful, but don't expect a barrel of laughs. You do get to see two great actresses together.

I went to a lot of trouble to get the subtitles in shape for this one, I hope my effort is appreciated. People should pay a lot more attention to Lanctot than they do.
